/>\n呢d 用黎修補<br />\n<br />\n一袋20kg 幾百蚊至1千蚊<br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:57:21.000Z","msg":"唔駛用到5星，要膠沙用士波令料最實惠，百零蚊包又硬"},{"pid":"02353cbf214a0b3685238550c1ffb3ef55dde80b","tid":1716002,"uid":218019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:00:06.000Z","msg":"一包英泥6包沙 石落唔落都得"},{"pid":"fa7e9e2483408051138dca3f437bd74c12dfc008","tid":1716002,"uid":284592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcb50e597eb31c6cf6745e2fb618857bfd032b45","tid":1716002,"uid":51740,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T08:55:46.000Z","msg":"師傅做嘢無咁仔細嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n基本上一包英泥撈6-7包沙，<br />\n有就加啲碎石，再有就加啲牛奶水，無就白膠漿得<br />\n<br />\n英泥沙石溝勻，挖個窿倒水，有牛奶水/膠漿就加入水，等幾分鐘翻勻就用得<br />\n<br />\n唔識做最難控制係水量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大約就係1份水泥+3-4份沙左右。<br />\n用水就係半份左右。做半乾濕沙就要再少D水。<br />\n一般叫師傅用泥斗量水，一泥斗水大約5L(好似係）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"995e2cee18ce03b5ae0269035f344d2a553c6863","tid":1716002,"uid":3179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"石屎完全乾硬要好多時間<br />\n最好用快乾性既英泥 加速凝固<br />\n但通常都比較貴"},{"pid":"186c8be27024bd2d52371548c89d76544f0acabf","tid":1716002,"uid":42304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"1包英泥45Kg 加6-7包沙 再加18L水就好硬<br />\n唔好淨英泥 會好易裂"},{"pid":"c9838f8faf63f847f1c3e136d5cf6b4b6e99a191","tid":1716002,"uid":161644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T09:06:05.000Z","msg":"要快乾既話落polarset"},{"pid":"e03df181e22bcc49630794b7fda4fe87283c313a","tid":1716002,"uid":52683,"like":0,"disl